ActNational Capital Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission ** Granting lease - Riverain Park **
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION enters into a forty-nine year lease with the City of Ottawa for the maintenance and the operation of the Riverain Park in Ottawa, Ontario.
